{"tid":677943,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全方位健身攻略","createTime":"2018-05-25T15:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T12:31:56.000Z","uid":170668,"like":26,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e13e1130e9c63e1fac64d312baea112215a2ea0c","tid":677943,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:34:36.000Z","msg":"小弟做咗gym都有1個月 今日想嚟分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議:<br />\n1.飲用奶粉(美贊臣呢個牌子功效較佳 價錢較便宜)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/232841_029ef0ba7fb0c302f8330867a3999129.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F232841_029ef0ba7fb0c302f8330867a3999129.png&h=a6a0bb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早餐:4-5隻雞蛋 切勿食用過多 否則膽固醇會過高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n午餐:大快活雞胸紅米飯 相信呢個唔洗多講<br />\n<br />\n2.操練 一定要持之以恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起身:時要做1set sit-up 每set 1下<br />\n中午:食完雞胸紅米飯可以舉一下鐵 鍛練胸肌<br />\n<br />\n以上係本人呢一個月嘅心得<br />\n<br />\n一個月成果:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/233342_75b2ec65d9c483f22c486d2c825817cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F233342_75b2ec65d9c483f22c486d2c825817cc.png&h=b2f61de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家可以一拳半件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746e13734917c2c197e7e6900db26e30892ef8cf","tid":677943,"uid":170668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"希望更多人受惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a34fbad2f4fcc97249c962eab6fa216f61ef01a","tid":677943,"uid":80795,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"巴打好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇話點減脂？"},{"pid":"fb3eb9f8024cf6851a16d63b6858e9d9761f3381","tid":677943,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"好想操到巴打你既身形<br />\n真係好靚"},{"pid":"bcd6afc7c966165f9e4ac463ba2936c94ee0e506","tid":677943,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a34fbad2f4fcc97249c962eab6fa216f61ef01a","tid":677943,"uid":80795,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"巴打好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇話點減脂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"做sit-up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bed5dd6e1a61249e3daeb0ad13691a2a6a26a2","tid":677943,"uid":54720,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"巴打有6粒lin?<br />\n點練出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8bba2c49938fe2e3154b1da293d929219965f2","tid":677943,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3eb9f8024cf6851a16d63b6858e9d9761f3381","tid":677943,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"好想操到巴打你既身形<br />\n真係好靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"前幾日去游水啲女𥄫實哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c45bf03b9fa34bd7266796dde25ba3906b5ac6a","tid":677943,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"好fit"},{"pid":"1391d084be642142101105310d14fd1c72ec3a91","tid":677943,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48bed5dd6e1a61249e